Paper: hep-th/9906165

Date: 1999-06-21

Title: Reply to the comment by D. Kreimer and E. Mielke

Authors: Osvaldo Chandia and Jorge Zanelli

Comments: 9 pages, revtex

We respond to the comment by Kreimer et. al. about the torsional contributionto the chiral anomaly in curved spacetimes. We discuss their claims and refuteits main conclusion.